@startuml akdb-observatory-sequence
title AKDB - Tiny Tool Observatory and Consumer Projection
actor Maintainer
participant "AKDB authoring surfaces" as Surface
database "AKDB database" as DB
participant "SAD/UML exporter" as Exporter
participant "Versioned architecture projection" as Projection
participant "Tiny Tool Observatory" as Observatory
participant "Other framework tools" as Consumers
Maintainer -> Surface : maintain architecture in AKDB
Surface -> DB : persist canonical records
Maintainer -> Exporter : export project architecture
Exporter -> DB : read all associated SAD/UML
Exporter -> Projection : deterministic files
Projection -> Observatory : architecture/product ingestion
Projection -> Consumers : stable integration artifact
note over DB,Projection
The database is authoring authority for DB-native SAD/UML.
Projection files are reviewable and distributable snapshots.
end note
@enduml
